Pre-Game Insights: Harambee Stars coach was bullish after the last round of fixtures saying “am not afraid of Cameroon “.
Miscellaneous Highlights: This will be another international break where Kenyans will not have a chance to watch their national team live due to lack of facilities.
Others: Kenya has never beaten Cameroon in 8 different encounters, with 4 draws and 4 losses, scoring 7 goals and allowing 14, Cameroon has played in seven finals, losing only two times.
